Steam-Force-Controller-OFF

Thanks to CMDR Zeeber for sharing this fix, which enabled his PlayStation Dualshock 4 controller to work with the mod.

1. Using the Steam app, click Elite Dangerous in your Library

2. On the right side of the screen, click the 'gear icon' (Manage), and then click Properties

3. Locate the drop-down menu, "Steam Input Per-Game Setting"

4. Select Forced Off

https://i.imgur.com/j8vhTWM.jpg

5. Press Close
